{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01BTH595rxjDCW1YSPpjn9k7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. I can see there's a ServiceAccount `crdb-cluster-sa`, a Role `crdb-cluster-role`, and a RoleBinding `crdb-cluster-rolebinding`. Now I'll create the necessary resources:\n\n1. Headless Service: `crdb-cluster` - for pod-to-pod DNS discovery\n2. Public Service: `crdb-cluster-public` - for external access\n3. StatefulSet: `crdb-cluster` with 3 replicas\n\nFor CockroachDB in insecure mode with 3 nodes, each pod needs to advertise its hostname and join all peers. \n\nI'm setting up the startup command so each node advertises itself using its pod DNS name and joins the cluster by connecting to all three initial nodes.\n\nFor the PodDisruptionBudget, I need to ensure at least 2 nodes stay available to maintain quorum across the 3-node cluster. Now I'll write out the complete YAML manifest.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":370,"cache_read_input_tokens":28761,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":370},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"438802b0-25b5-4246-b6e7-c7e015cbce09","uuid":"9b3ae2df-d3cc-4b3d-8d15-efae6d8a98e3","request_id":"req_011CcL9xADPKroha54qQmFw7"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01BTH595rxjDCW1YSPpjn9k7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"RBAC is ready. I'll deploy the headless service, public service, StatefulSet, and a PodDisruptionBudget to protect quorum."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":370,"cache_read_input_tokens":28761,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":370},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"438802b0-25b5-4246-b6e7-c7e015cbce09","uuid":"57a7ade2-531b-4172-975f-c4bf0c6bb809","request_id":"req_011CcL9xADPKroha54qQmFw7"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01BTH595rxjDCW1YSPpjn9k7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_014CCXHhZ1hTLdRy5u77WzJy","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"kubectl apply -f - <<'EOF'\n---\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Service\nmetadata:\n  name: crdb-cluster\n  namespace: cockroachdb\n  labels:\n    app: crdb-cluster\n  annotations:\n    service.alpha.kubernetes.io/tolerate-unready-endpoints: \"true\"\nspec:\n  clusterIP: None\n  publishNotReadyAddresses: true\n  ports:\n  - name: grpc\n    port: 26257\n    targetPort: 26257\n  - name: http\n    port: 8080\n    targetPort: 8080\n  selector:\n    app: crdb-cluster\n---\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Service\nmetadata:\n  name: crdb-cluster-public\n  namespace: cockroachdb\n  labels:\n    app: crdb-cluster\nspec:\n  ports:\n  - name: grpc\n    port: 26257\n    targetPort: 26257\n  - name: http\n    port: 8080\n    targetPort: 8080\n  selector:\n    app: crdb-cluster\n---\napiVersion: policy/v1\nkind: PodDisruptionBudget\nmetadata:\n  name: crdb-cluster-pdb\n  namespace: cockroachdb\nspec:\n  minAvailable: 2\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      app: crdb-cluster\n---\napiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: StatefulSet\nmetadata:\n  name: crdb-cluster\n  namespace: cockroachdb\nspec:\n  serviceName: crdb-cluster\n  replicas: 3\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      app: crdb-cluster\n  updateStrategy:\n    type: RollingUpdate\n  podManagementPolicy: Parallel\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: crdb-cluster\n    spec:\n      serviceAccountName: crdb-cluster-sa\n      terminationGracePeriodSeconds: 60\n      containers:\n      - name: cockroachdb\n        image: cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.0\n        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n        ports:\n        - name: grpc\n          containerPort: 26257\n        - name: http\n          containerPort: 8080\n        env:\n        - name: POD_NAME\n          valueFrom:\n            fieldRef:\n              fieldPath: metadata.name\n        command:\n        - /bin/bash\n        - -ecx\n        - |\n          exec /cockroach/cockroach start \\\n            --insecure \\\n            --advertise-addr=${POD_NAME}.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local \\\n            --http-addr=0.0.0.0:8080 \\\n            --listen-addr=0.0.0.0:26257 \\\n            --join=crdb-cluster-0.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local,crdb-cluster-1.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local,crdb-cluster-2.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local \\\n            --cache=.25 \\\n            --max-sql-memory=.25\n        readinessProbe:\n          httpGet:\n            path: /health?ready=1\n            port: 8080\n          initialDelaySeconds: 10\n          periodSeconds: 5\n          failureThreshold: 2\n        livenessProbe:\n          httpGet:\n            path: /health\n            port: 8080\n          initialDelaySeconds: 30\n          periodSeconds: 5\n        volumeMounts:\n        - name: datadir\n          mountPath: /cockroach/cockroach-data\n  volumeClaimTemplates:\n  - metadata:\n      name: datadir\n    spec:\n      accessModes: [\"ReadWriteOnce\"]\n      resources:\n        requests:\n          storage: 10Gi\nEOF","description":"Deploy CockroachDB headless service, public service, PDB, and StatefulSet"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":370,"cache_read_input_tokens":28761,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":370},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"438802b0-25b5-4246-b6e7-c7e015cbce09","uuid":"ed016eae-94f3-4131-990c-ec03a66ba8d6","request_id":"req_011CcL9xADPKroha54qQmFw7"}
